As the values of nodes are in range of 1 to 9 . So, we dont need to store all the values in a vector , to improve the space complexity we will just store how many 1's , 2's , 3's ....... 9's are present in current path , for which we need a vector of only size 10; 
Now if more than 1 value is present in odd number then we can form a palindrome of it.
Else we can form a palindrome from it.

